appName: HickonuQ "The Rise of the Legendary Farmer"
displayName: HickonuQ "The Rise of the Legendary Farmer"
display_name: HickonuQ "The Rise of the Legendary Farmer"
display_long_description:
# Grab it, hold it, pull it out! An MR harvesting puzzle for everywhere!

**"HickonuQ: The Rise of the Legendary Farmer ’** pulls vegetables out of your living room, in the park, on the road, anywhere they keep growing, with your bare hands! Find the right moment and aim for the best harvest!  
The Rise of the Legendary Farmer** is an MR action harvesting puzzle game set in a real space!

---

- **Harvesting Tips**: Grab and pull to complete the harvest! If you let go, you can immediately sell it and make a profit.
- **Thrilling timing**: Too early and you lose, too late and you rot. Aim for perfect timing and you'll be a god farmer!
- **Exhilarating physical harvest**: control the flying seeds and experience the joy of a bountiful harvest.
- **FREE MR PUZZLE**: Once you start, you'll be hooked!

Translated with www.DeepL.com/Translator (free version)
